### 列文章（分页）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?page=1&size=10

### 按标题搜
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?title=Spring

### 发文章
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "学 Spring Boot 第 1 天",
  "content": "今天学了 IoC 和自动装配"
}

### 看文章详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### 删文章（联动减用户文章数）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### 发评论
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "articleId": 1,
  "userId": 2,
  "content": "学到了"
}

### 看文章下评论
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments?articleId=1
